      "panel-7": {
        "kind": "Panel",
        "spec": {
          "id": 7,
          "title": "User Process Time ",
          "description": "This metric tracks how much (as a percentage) user level programs take up computing power in the CPU. It's important to individually track how much time the CPU spends in user mode to see where to optimize in the future. Say the percentage passed a certain threshold. Then, we would know that application code needs to be optimized rather than the problem being an OS problem.",
